      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/bhp-has-a-week-to-convince-anglo-its-south-african-plan-can-work</link>
      <description><![CDATA[必和必拓集团刚刚赢得了额外一周的时间来说服英美资源集团 (Anglo American Plc) 实施其 490 亿美元的收购计划。但这家全球最大的矿商仍必须解决该交易中最棘手的障碍：南非该怎么办？]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/bhp-has-a-week-to-convince-anglo-its-south-african-plan-can-work</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 21:40:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投票前，约翰·赫斯亲自致电投资者支持雪佛龙交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/john-hess-personally-calls-investors-to-support-chevron-deal-days-before-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，以他的姓氏命名的石油公司的老板约翰·赫斯 (John Hess) 正在与股东直接进行对话，以确保为雪佛龙公司 (Chevron Corp.) 530 亿美元的收购提供足够的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-22/john-hess-personally-calls-investors-to-support-chevron-deal-days-before-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 May 2024 20:52:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
